_sText:
Zombie have invaded an oil company territory in Alaska. Now everyone must hide and try to survive. Many places to hide and many high places that zombie might have trouble reaching.

Features:
-Great Barricade spots
-Many High Places
-Box Fort

Authors:
GabrielPapaK

Authors from Prefabs Used:
Law
NatalyaAF
Depredator

Time: 15 Hours

Install:
Extract the map file (zm_alaskan_survival_gpk.bsp), also the (zm_alaskan_survival_gpk.bsp.bak) and the navigation file (zm_alaskan_survival_gpk.nav) to your Counter-Strike maps folder (Usually located here:C:\Program Files\steam\steamapps\***YOURNAMEHERE***\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps).

Hope you all enjoy and have fun...
This is only version 1 for now... I WILL make a version 2 when I have time.
